		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Blood Addiction",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>Whenever the bruxa is in presence of a fey's blood, or sees a fey that is taking bleed damage, the bruxa must attempt at a @Check[will|dc:35] save or enter in blood induced frenzy state for 1 minute.</p><p>While in this frenzy, the bruxa gains a +1 status bonus to all its attacks roll and damage rolls, but is considered @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Off-Guard} while in frenzy. This frenzy lasts for 1 minute or until the bruxa falls @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious} or slain (whichever happens first).</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.monster-homebrewery.effects.Item.S7vdzusXllcPgGDk]{Effect: Blood Frenzy}</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
